{"tid":1786666,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"扭曲圍棋黑白子 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-17T09:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T09:48:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a495446a83bab09c7e7768f9bb9e2e1e8a0578af","tid":1786666,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:47:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191217/20826259/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F20826259%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0r9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=9a60ef62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F20826259%2F&h=828f16f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191217/20826259/</a><br />\n<br />\n扭曲圍棋黑白子 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191217/large/1576485410_cfd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191217%2Flarge%2F1576485410_cfd5.jpg&h=b2fd0d4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我對集郵沒什麼興趣──不過對郵票某些奇特改動卻甚關注。<br />\n<br />\n香港郵政明年推出12套特別郵票，有「鼠年」、「廿四節氣」、配合4月兒童節的「弈棋」、武打巨星「李小龍」&hellip;&hellip;等系列。<br />\n<br />\n「棋樂無窮」的設計早已在10月公佈，6款兒童郵票主題是：象棋、鬥獸棋、飛行棋、國際象棋、波子棋及圍棋，都是大家兒時童趣。其設計意念是棋藝能夠訓練人集中和專注，引發思考想像，變化多端勝負莫測激發應付逆境的能力。<br />\n<br />\n今年對孩子而言，是複雜又催促成熟的一年，他們不但在逆權抗爭運動中面對各種挑戰，分明是非黑白正邪善惡，還發揮團結互助精神，過程創意無限，早已超越天真棋藝。<br />\n<br />\n近日當局宣傳，<span style=\"color: orange;\">圍棋郵票中小孩原來的黑衣和白衣已改色！</span>這國粹棋藝，使用格狀棋盤和黑白二色棋子進行對弈，遊戲策略成份極高，時間由數十分鐘至數天甚至一生不能解局，數千年來圍棋只用黑子白子，<span style=\"color: orange;\">沒料到香港郵政對「黑白」那麼敏感，小孩衣服改為啡、黃（囚衣之色嗎？）</span>，令人質疑因迎合極權而自我審查，扭曲原意，破壞了圍棋之美。既然黑白不分、不明，特色不敢表現，索性別選「圍棋」好了──香港變成這樣，令人傷感。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"a7fed2fdafb5646d3be601c88724c0224c506e33","tid":1786666,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RU8EhU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRU8EhU3.jpg&h=c3f3defe&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}